('46','Kuwaiti Zakat House','بيت الزكاة الكويتي','kuwaiti-zakat-house','بيت-الزكاة-الكويتي','<p><span class=\"VIiyi\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b C1N51c\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"ar\" data-phrase-index=\"0\" data-number-of-phrases=\"1\"><span class=\"Q4iAWc\">The Zakat House is an independent governmental body whose mission is to collect and develop Zakat resources and charity and spend them locally and externally in accordance with the provisions of Islamic Sharia.</span></span></span></p>','<p>بيت الزكاة هيئة حكومية مستقلة رسالتها جمع وتنمية موارد الزكاة والخيرات 
