('59','Humanitarian Access Association','جمعية الوصول الإنساني','humanitarian-access-association','جمعية-الوصول-الإنساني','<div class=\"J0lOec\"><span class=\"VIiyi\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"ar\" data-phrase-index=\"0\" data-number-of-phrases=\"1\"><span class=\"Q4iAWc\">The association works in the following fields: sustainable development, combating poverty, child and youth care. The association also provides health services, social and educational care, emergency relief and women\'s development.</span></span></span><span class=\"zEswK\"></span></div><p></p>','<p>تعمل الجمعية فى المجالات التالية التنمية المستدامة ومكافحة الفقر ورعاية 
الطفولة والشباب ـ ايضا تقدم الجمعية الخدمات الصحية والرعاية الاجتماعية 
والتعليمية والاغاثة الطارئة وتنمية المراة .</p>','1663157013logo.png','1663157013cover.png','','<p><span class=\"VIiyi\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"ar\" data-phrase-index=\"0\" data-number-of-phrases=\"3\"><span class=\"Q4iAWc\">Head of the organization: Mr. Yahya Hassan Al-Daba</span></span><span class=\"JLqJ4b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"ar\" data-phrase-index=\"1\" data-number-of-phrases=\"3\"><span class=\"Q4iAWc\">
</span></span></span><span class=\"VIiyi\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"ar\" data-phrase-index=\"1\" data-number-of-phrases=\"3\"><span class=\"Q4iAWc\">
</span></span><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"ar\" data-phrase-index=\"2\" data-number-of-phrases=\"3\"><span class=\"Q4iAWc\">Secretary-General of the Organization: Dr. Abdel Wasi Al-Wasei</span></span></span></p>','<p>رئيس المنظمة: ا/ يحيى حسن الدباء<br><br>الأمين العام للمنظمة: د/ عبد الواسع الواسعي<br></p>','967739955011','967739955011','admin@admin.com','aden','عدن','https://www.Facebook.com/','https://www.Twitter.com/','https://www.Instagram.com/','https://www.Youtube.com/','1','0','','0','1','0','2022-09-14 12:03:33','2022-10-02 10:37:12','','16');

